'''沉船'''是[[輪船|輪船]]沉沒後的殘骸，可因[[海难|海难]]、軍事行動等原因做成。1999年1月，有研究估計全球有約三百萬艘沉船<ref>Angela Croome (January 16, 1999). “[https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg16121696-000-sinking-fast/ Sinking fast] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg16121696-000-sinking-fast/ |date=20171225203002 }}”, New Scientist, Volume 161, Issue 2169, pp. 49.</ref>，並獲[[联合国教育、科学及文化组织|联合国教育、科学及文化组织]]<ref>“Sinking fast”, [https://open.unido.org/api/documents/4813394/download/MARINE%20INDUSTRIAL%20TECHNOLOGY%201%20AND%202-1999.%20EMERGING%20TECHNOLOGY%20SERIES%20(22293.en) Marine Industrial Technology, 1 and 2/1999] {{Wayback|url=https://open.unido.org/api/documents/4813394/download/MARINE%20INDUSTRIAL%20TECHNOLOGY%201%20AND%202-1999.%20EMERGING%20TECHNOLOGY%20SERIES%20(22293.en) |date=20210224123545 }}, Emerging Technology Series, United Nations Industrial Development Organization, pp. 58.</ref><ref>Lucia Iglesias Kuntz (June 12, 2002), “[http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID=3304&URL_DO=DO_TOPIC&URL_SECTION=201.html UNESCO urges the Americas to join the underwater heritage convention] {{Wayback|url=http://portal.unesco.org/en/ev.php-URL_ID%3D3304%26URL_DO%3DDO_TOPIC%26URL_SECTION%3D201.html |date=20171226020827 }}”, UNESCO Media Services.</ref>及其他組織支持<ref>“[https://sha.org/publication-links/newsletter/newsletter-archives/ Lisbon Resolution] {{Wayback|url=https://sha.org/publication-links/newsletter/newsletter-archives/ |date=20171225203031 }}”, Society for Historical Archaeology Newsletter, Summer 1999, Volume 32, Number 2, pp. 31.</ref>。

較有歷史的沉船常受[[沉船考古學|沉船考古學]]研究，以便了解當地的民土風情。沉船亦為[[休闲潜水|休闲潜水]]的常見目的地。部分沉船上則有貴重貨物可供打撈。超過一百年的沉船受{{tsl|en|UNESCO Convention on the Protection of the Underwater Cultural Heritage|聯合國教科文組織水下文化遺產保護公約}}保護<ref>{{cite web|title=Convention on the protection of the Underwater Cultural Heritage - Text of the 2001 Convention|editor=UNESCO|url=http://www.unesco.org/new/en/culture/themes/underwater-cultural-heritage/2001-convention/official-text|access-date=2016-02-04|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410192451/http://www.unesco.org/new/en/culture/themes/underwater-cultural-heritage/2001-convention/official-text/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

